Fs,\nlending credibility that this two dimensional optical luminosity-HI mass\ndistribution is an accurate representation of the volume density distribution\nof galaxies in the local universe. We also note that our agreement with HIMFs\nfrom other surveys is dependent on accounting for all systematic differences\nsuch as selection method, Hubble constant and HI flux scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2018 06:52:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
