rd soil\ncompositions. Linear regressions between input and output soil water contents,\ninferred from simulated $^{40}K$ and $^{208}Tl$ gamma signals, provide\nexcellent results demonstrating the capability of the proposed method in\nestimating soil water content with an average uncertainty <1%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2018 15:50:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-11"}
